author: rvesse
msg: Further work on implicit left join optimization (JENA-473)
This commit relaxes the lineraization restriction on left join linearization to allow linearizing across assignments provided that
all variables used to compute the assignment are themselves defined on the RHS
Includes new tests for optimization and for join classification
